---
title: Ponzu Plum Chicken with Cauliflower Rice & Sesame Roasted Broccoli
description: Peter Piper plucked a plate of ponzu plum pork chops. At least, we bet he would have once he got a taste of tonight’s dinner. It stars an indulgent, flavorful sauce made with ponzu, plum jam, and Sriracha—thickened just enough to coat juicy pork chops. You won’t be mad if some of that tangy-sweet sauce drips onto the tender cauliflower rice and sesame roasted broccoli. And what happened to our friend Peter Piper? He polished off that plate of ponzu plum pork chops.
